(The training pipeline does the following:) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 754 Tm
(1. Generates synthetic traffic data for benign and malicious patterns.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 740 Tm
(2. Splits the data into train and test sets using stratified sampling.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 726 Tm
(3. Applies SMOTE to balance the training data.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 712 Tm
(4. Fits a StandardScaler plus Logistic Regression pipeline.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 698 Tm
(5. Predicts probabilities on the test set.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 684 Tm
(6. Tunes the decision threshold over multiple values.) Tj
ET
BT
/Helvetica 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48 670 Tm
(7. Saves the trained model and metadata as joblib artifacts.) Tj
ET
